<plot>July 1952. A gentleman who is due to take the train comes running to the station only to miss it. He explains to the station master that he is a hundred years late! Puzzled by this unusual statement, the station master listens to the man's explanations. In fact, the man had fallen asleep and dreamed he had boarded an old-fashioned train which took a hundred years to reach its destination...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?098098</url></doc>
